### Assessment API Test Examples
### Use this file with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@token = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Create Skill
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/assessment/Skills
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "JavaScript",
  "status": true
}

### 2. Create College
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/assessment/College
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "MIT",
  "status": true
}

### 3. Create Job
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/assessment/Jobs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Software Engineer",
  "status": true
}

### 4. Create Industry
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/assessment/Industries
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Technology",
  "status": true
}

### 5. Get All Skills
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/assessment/Skills
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Get All Skills with Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/assessment/Skills?search=java
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Get All Active Skills
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/assessment/Skills?status=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Get Single Skill by ID (replace ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/assessment/Skills/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Update Skill (replace ID)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/assessment/Skills/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "JavaScript ES6",
  "status": true
}

### 10. Toggle Status (replace ID)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/assessment/Skills/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": false
}

### 11. Delete Skill (replace ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/assessment/Skills/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

